{"title":"天天的钢琴","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":128,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/165#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=165","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/165/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/165/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/165"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"天天开始弹奏钢琴了。他的钢琴由 $N$ 个琴键组成，每个键有一个权值 $xi$ ,当天天开始弹琴时，他同时按 $K$ 个不同的键。但是这个钢琴十分古怪，在他同时按了 $K$ 个键之后，我们只能听到**具有最大权值**的那个键。现在天天准备试试这个钢琴 $K$ 个键的所有组合，他想要知道将要听到琴声的权值和。因为结果会很大，所以输出mod 1000000007之后的结果。\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行两个整数 $N$ ， $K$ 。(1<= $N$ <=100000,1<= $K$ <=50).\r\n\r\n下一行由 $N$ 个整数xi组成(0<= $xi$ <=1000000000).\r\n"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一个整数 表示sum%P的结果"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"####【样例输入】\r\n```\r\n5 3\r\n\r\n2 4 2 3 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n####【样例输出】\r\n```\r\n39\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"####题目来源 ： **2016 COCI#5  **\r\n/w\\   开动脑筋想一想~"}]}